a=\sqrt{x},b=\sqrt{y},c=\sqrt{s}
g(t^2)=\dfrac{f(t^2)-f(c^2)}{t^2-c^2}=\dfrac{1+ct}{(1-c^2)(1-t^2)(t+c)}
